Required packages (Ubuntu 11.04):
libboost-dev
libboost-thread-dev
freetype-dev
expat-dev

Third Party Sources:
https://GordonSmith@github.com/GordonSmith/FireBreath-1.git (Branch firebreath-1.5)
http://www.graphviz.org/pub/graphviz/stable/SOURCES/graphviz-2.26.3.tar.gz (You may need to run ./Configure)
svn co https://agg.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/agg agg svn co https://agg.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/agg agg

cmake variables that need to be set (for source locations above):
FIREBREATHSRC_DIR
AGGSRC_DIR
GRAPHVIZSRC_DIR

